buildings.description: The Engineering Building is dedicated to programs in computer, electronics, electrical, and other applied engineering fields. It features specialized laboratories such as circuits labs, computer labs, workshop areas, and innovation spaces. Students conduct hands-on experiments, prototype development, and technical research here. The building also hosts most engineering lectures, faculty offices, and project-based learning sessions.
